"content": "<h2>Driving out demons</h2>\n<h3>In Jesus Christ's ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:34\">MRK 1:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:16\">MAT 8:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:32-Matt9:33\">MAT 9:32–9:33</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:14\">LUK 11:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:39\">MRK 1:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:32\">LUK 13:32</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ accused of using satanic power to drive out demons</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:24-Matt12:28\">MAT 12:24–12:28</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:22-Mark3:26\">MRK 3:22–3:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:15-Luke11:20\">LUK 11:15–11:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:34\">MAT 9:34</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ commissioned his disciples to drive out demons</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:1\">MAT 10:1</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:1\">LUK 9:1</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:8\">MAT 10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:15\">MRK 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:13\">MRK 6:13</a></p>\n<h3>The failure of the disciples to drive out demons</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:18\">MRK 9:18</a></p>\n<h3>Others attempted to use Jesus Christ's authority</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:49\">LUK 9:49</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:13\">ACT 19:13</a></p>\n<h3>Driving out demons is no substitute for obedience to the will of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:22\">MAT 7:22</a></p>\n<h3>Driving out demons and Satan as an aspect of Jesus Christ's overall ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:31\">JHN 12:31</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Driving out people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num33:51-Num33:52\">NUM 33:51–33:52</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:11\">EXO 10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:2\">PSA 44:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:26\">PRO 19:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:10\">PRO 22:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:2\">JER 29:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:12\">MAT 21:12</a></p>",
